{"tid":144131,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"奧斯卡玩手機搞到頒錯獎，會唔會畀人炒？","createTime":"2017-03-05T07:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T08:26:43.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8533862df3656a5004519c15019d24f6802ba457","tid":144131,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:32:58.000Z","msg":"原來頒錯最佳電影獎的源頭是負責點票及核實成績的PwC會計師事務所合夥人Brian Cullinan。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此人並非普通合夥人，而是美國PwC董事會主席。</span><br />\n<br />\n他在傳遞得獎信封時在玩手機，在Twitter打緊卡，把名單掉亂了。聽說大會永不錄用該會計師及其事務所，而Cullinan更被跟蹤及收死亡恐嚇。"},{"pid":"0e99b1f5ebf704dea2572c69ba9c0007231a6e15","tid":144131,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:33:37.000Z","msg":"你地估條友要唔要咩鑊？"},{"pid":"ba2ef22adf36dd7f3b97d73dce318a062ca04b7d","tid":144131,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"孭咗啦<br />\n不過係以後唔使佢哋負責頒獎相關活動"},{"pid":"bd82997d1f14318627971db1d045406eab24cd75","tid":144131,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"收死亡恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3605a04be723b537b31270e0f98ce7c2f70a265d","tid":144131,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>孭咗啦<br />\n不過係以後唔使佢哋負責頒獎相關活動</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n玩手機果個唔使畀人炒，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係普通職員，神早就無得撈啦"}]}